text: Shareena Clanton (born 1990) is an Australian film, television and theatre actress. She is known for her role as Doreen Anderson on the television drama series Wentworth (2013–2017).Wentworth website Shareena Clanton Retrieved July 1, 2015 ==Biography== Clanton was born in Perth, Western Australia. She is of Wangatha, Yamatji, Noongar and Gidja descent. She currently resides in Melbourne, Victoria. == Filmography == ===Film=== {| class="wikitable sortable" |- ! Year ! Title !
